---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Earthquake-Resistant Homes: Building Safer Structures in Nepal";
const description = "Learn about essential design and structural elements that make homes in Nepal resilient to earthquakes, ensuring safety and peace of mind for homeowners.";
const date = "2024-04-01";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="blog-post">
    <header>
      <p class="date">{new Date(date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
        year: 'numeric',
        month: 'long',
        day: 'numeric'
      })}</p>
      <h1>{title}</h1>
    </header>

    <img 
      src="https://arcmaxarchitect.com/sites/default/files/styles/banner_image_1024x585/public/weekend_home_and_row_house_design.jpg?itok=8AJKyNxB"
      alt="Earthquake-Resistant House Design"
      class="hero-image"
    />

    <div class="content">
      <p class="lead">Nepal is located in a seismically active region, making earthquake-resistant homes essential for safety. By using specific design strategies, homeowners can ensure resilience in their structures.</p>

      <h2>Key Earthquake-Resistant Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Flexible foundations to absorb seismic shock</li>
        <li>Reinforced concrete frames</li>
        <li>Cross-bracing for stability</li>
        <li>Use of lightweight construction materials</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Smart Construction Techniques</h2>
      <p>These building techniques can enhance a homeâ€™s resistance to earthquakes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Base isolation systems</li>
        <li>Proper wall connections</li>
        <li>Roof and wall reinforcements</li>
        <li>Regular structural inspections</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Building Codes and Regulations</h2>
      <p>Following Nepal's building codes helps ensure earthquake resilience:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Compliance with National Building Code (NBC)</li>
        <li>Using certified materials and practices</li>
        <li>Involving structural engineers for safety assurance</li>
        <li>Regular audits for structural integrity</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
<style>
  .blog-post {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .date {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .content {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }
  img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  ul {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  a {
    color: #3498db;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
